{"tha-ap78:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap78:0.2":"Nagasamalavagga ","tha-ap78:0.3":"6 Tinasantharadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap78:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap78:1.2":"mahajatassaro ahu; ","tha-ap78:1.3":"Satapattehi sanchanno, ","tha-ap78:1.4":"nanasakunamalayo. ","tha-ap78:2.1":"Tamhi nhatva ca pitva ca, ","tha-ap78:2.2":"avidure vasamaham; ","tha-ap78:2.3":"Addasam samananaggam, ","tha-ap78:2.4":"gacchantam anilanjase. ","tha-ap78:3.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap78:3.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap78:3.3":"Abbhato oruhitvana, ","tha-ap78:3.4":"bhumiyamthasi tavade. ","tha-ap78:4.1":"Visanena tinam gayha, ","tha-ap78:4.2":"nisidanamadasaham; ","tha-ap78:4.3":"Nisidi bhagava tattha, ","tha-ap78:4.4":"tisso lokagganayako. ","tha-ap78:5.1":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap78:5.2":"avandi lokanayakam; ","tha-ap78:5.3":"Patikutiko apasakkim, ","tha-ap78:5.4":"nijjhayanto mahamunim. ","tha-ap78:6.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap78:6.2":"nimmanam upapajjaham; ","tha-ap78:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap78:6.4":"santharassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap78:7.1":"Ito dutiyake kappe, ","tha-ap78:7.2":"miga sammatakhattiyo; ","tha-ap78:7.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap78:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap78:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap78:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap78:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap78:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinasantharadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap78:10.1":"Tinasantharadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}